LeaveMyKidzAlone
{{pixplz}}

LeaveMyKidzAlone is a forum operated by notorious [[pedophilia|pervert]] [[Ryle Garamonde]]. It originally started as a [[cult|user group]] on [[Vampire Freaks]] and became very popular, but that came to an end when it was discovered that Ryle had been soliciting [[noodz]] from, and [[cybersex|camming]] with, [[jailbait|underage]] group members in exchange for [[mod]] positions in his user group. Prior to that, he had been using the user group as a forum for [[internet poor|panhandling]] via [[PayPal]] donations.

After the [[delete fucking everything|deletion]] of the user group on Vampire Freaks, Ryle founded a stand-alone site and a user group on [[Vampire Shitty]].

